<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yạ yswʿ lyk kl ạ̉yạmnạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (yạ yswʿ lyk kl ạ̉yạmnạ .. wkl ạlly jạy qdạmnạ
 mlkwtk ymly̱ ạ̉ḥlạmnạ .. wnwrk hạysẖʿ fynạ)2
 ạlqrạr- (rwḥk jwạnạ wwsṭynạ .. wtʿạl wạtmjd fynạ)2
 wnʿysẖ ạ̉yạmnạ wlyạlynạ .. nsẖhd ʿn ḥbk yạ fạdynạ
 2- (ạstkẖdm ḥbk jwạnạ .. wrwḥ qdsk ạlly mlạnạ
 myn ʿlynạ wạnt mʿạnạ .. yạ yswʿ wḥdnạ wqwynạ)2
 3- (bnḥṭ qlwbnạ qdạmk .. tmsḥ wtkrs ạ̉wlạdk
 yạ yswʿ wrynạ ạ̉mjạdk .. wyswʿ ybqy̱ wạḍḥ fynạ)2</lyrics>
